# Hygiene Check (Cursor)

Run a comprehensive workspace hygiene check and report actionable results.

## Execution
- Execute the workspace script non-interactively:
  - `~/.agent-os/scripts/workspace-hygiene-check.sh`
- If the script is missing, first install Agent OS base: 
  - `curl -sSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/carmandale/agent-os/main/setup.sh | bash`

## Report Format
- Provide the report using the summary template from the instructions
- Include actual command outputs where relevant (git status, branch, GH status)
- Use clear visual indicators (✅❌⚠️)

